<p>Dear <%= user.username %></p>

<p>Thank you very much for your registration to LAYA, the accessible learning platform!</p>

<p>Before you can go on to LAYA, please verify your e-mail address by clicking on the link
    below:</p>

<strong><a href="<%= protocol + '://' + host + ':' + port + '/verify?uid=' + user.id +
    '&token=' + user.verificationToken %>">Click</a></strong>

<p>If you didn't register for LAYA, you don't have to do anything: We delete
    unverified E-mail addresses after 48 hours.</p>
